{
  "stem": "11611.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somewhere along the-- that time, we had Bertrand Russell there too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I also attended Russell's lectures.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I attended everything that was around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Extremely familiar.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was an area in which I was interested and also was part of my curricular studies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For example, somewhere around the age of 16, I read from cover to cover.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm probably one of the few people alive today who ever did read it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a pretty good idea of what the Nazis were up to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not while I was at the University-- not in-- not up to 1940, no.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although by that time, we had refugees turning up as students-- German Jews, primarily, who were-- had been extremely well connected in Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, these were people who had titles, who were associated with the Kaiser's court, who were well-to-do, who were more German than they were either American or Jewish.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Any group that I was connected with was anti-Nazi.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no question of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- it was after college, at the law school, that I became more active, although not tremendously active.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "While I was at law school, there were a bunch of Anglophiles who had an interest in supporting the British against the Germans in 1940 and '41, and I became a part of that group.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The notable figure there was Bill Bundy, who was a classmate of mine, who later became a director of the CIA.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Harvard.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1940.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the law library at Harvard Law School.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Surprise.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not altogether surprise, and I'll tell you why.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was sitting up in the-- there was a typewriting enclave where you could type your notes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I noticed a big stir in the middle of the library, which was unusual.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
